    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Phenacorhamdia roxoi, MZUSP 125819, 63.8 mm SL, holotype, from São Paulo State, Botucatu Municipality, Córrego Hortelã, rio Paranapanema, Upper Paraná River basin. (a) dorsal view, (b) lateral view and (c) ventral view." ;
