    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Left column Phenacorhamdia roxoi, paratypes: a) LBP 29850, 69.0 mm SL; b) LBP 28707, 50.0 mm SL; c) LBP 28707, 42.6 mm SL. Right column, Penacorhamdia tenebrosa, topotypes, LBP 29845, d) 45.7 mm SL; e) 37.4 mm SL f) 30.5 mm SL." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4301922/files/figure.png" ;
